    <h1>llms.txt</h1>
    <p class="description">A plain-text file at your site root that tells AI crawlers what your content contains, what can be summarised, and how to attribute it. The <strong>robots.txt for AI systems</strong> — small file, big visibility impact.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
