            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Early signals in AI-driven referral traffic typically appear within 4-8 weeks. Meaningful lift in AI citation frequency usually takes 3-6 months as AI crawlers re-index the file and models are retrained or updated.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

